• Hyaluronic acid: Helps retain your skin’s natural moisture\n• Niacinamide: Helps calm your skin\n• Non-comedogenic, gentle, and fragrance-free\n• Developed with dermatologists','face wash, cleanser, face cleanser, acne face wash, hyaluronic acid, face wash for oily skin, cleanser for oily skin, Cerave foaming cleanser, ceramides, cleanser, Normal to Oily Skin','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,78,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
