elp restore and maintain the skin’s natural barrier\n• Hyaluronic acid: Helps retain the skin’s natural moisture\n• Non-comedogenic, non-irritating and fragrance-free\n• Developed with dermatologists\n• Accepted by the National Eczema Association','face wash, cleanser, face cleanser, hyaluronic acid, Cerave hydrating cleanser, face wash for dry skin, ceramides, cleanser, Normal to Dry Skin','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,76,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
