SODIUM EDTA, TETRASODIUM EDTA, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, PHYTOSPHINGOSINE, XANTHAN GUM, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN','• Gentle exfoliation for normal, dry and rough skin \n• Effectively cleanses to remove dirt and oil\n• Salicylic acid helps exfoliate for soft, smooth skin\n• Enriched with antioxidant vitamin D\n• Ceramides: Help restore and maintain the skin’s natural barrier\n• Hyaluronic acid: Helps retain the skin’s natural moisture\n• Niacinamide: Helps calm skin\n• Non-comedogenic, allergy tested and fragrance-free\n• Developed with dermatologists','salicylic acid, face wash, cleanser, face cleanser, salicylic acid cleanser, Cerave salicylic acid cleanser , ceramides, cleanser, Normal, dry and rough skin','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,67,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
