\n• Antioxidant, to protect from oxidative stress induced by pollution & infrared-A.','sunscreen, sun block, sunscreen for face, spf, sunblock cream,sun cream, la roche posay sunscreen, anti-ageing, Sun Protection, All skin types, Anthelios','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,65,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
