n sunscreen mist for oily and blemish-prone skin prone to sensitivity\n• For Oily Skin\n• Invisible, matte-finish texture\n• Can be worn over or under make-up. Has 3-second application. No white marks.\n• Very water resistant.\n•  With Perfume, paraben-free.','sunscreen, sun block, sunscreen for face, spf, sunblock cream,sun cream, sunscreen for oily skin, la roche posay sunscreen, sunscreen spray, Sun Protection, Oily, Anthelios','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,63,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
