 for efficacy and tolerance.','anti aging serum, serum, retinol serum, face serum, la roche posay retinol serum, serum, Sensitive, Redermic','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,59,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
