CASSOSIDE • MANGANESE GLUCONATE • ISOHEXADECANE • SODIUM ACRYLATES CROSSPOLYMER-2 • SILICA • 2-OLEAMIDO-1,3-OCTADECANEDIOL • PERLITE • DROMETRIZOLE TRISILOXANE • POLOXAMER 338 • DISODIUM EDTA • COPPER GLUCONATE • CAPRYLYL GLYCOL • POLYSORBATE 80 • ACRYLAMIDE/SODIUM ACRYLOYLDIMETHYLTAURATE COPOLYMER • ACRYLATES/C10-30 ALKYL ACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER • BHT • TOCOPHEROL • PHENOXYETHANOL','After 1 month of clinical test, patients claim that Cicaplast Baume B5 SPF50 :\nReduced burning sensations for 91%\nReduced tightness for 88%\nReduced pain sensations, tingling for 75%\nReduced redness for 93 %\n*use test on 44 and 40 volunteers, during 1 month','Body moisturiser, All Skin Types, Cicaplast','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,95,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('la-roche-posay-cicaplast-baume-b5-ultra-reparing-16809','La Roche Posay Cicaplast Baume B5+ Ultra Reparing Soothing Balm 40ml','La Roche-Posay','Body Care',17.01,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'cicaplast','Ultra-repairing soothing balm accelerated repair from day 1','La Roche Posay Cicaplast Baume B5+ is a multi-purpose repairing balm that soothes and protects the whole family’s sensitive or irritated skin. Suitable for adults, children and babies, it can be used on all kinds of everyday skin irritations and minor injuries and is ideal for use on sensitive skin.','3337875816809','320MB4975','40 ml','How to use: \nApply twice daily to pre-washed and dried skin. Can be applied in a generous layer.\nCan be applied to body, face and lips. Avoid the eye contour area.','TRIBIOMA, AQUA POSAE FILIFORMIS, PANTHENOL, MADECASSOSIDE, ZINC, AMNGANESE GLUCONATE, SHEA BUTTER, CLYCERIN, SPRING WATER','• Ultra-repairing soothing balm accelerated repair from day 1\n\n• Multi-purpose repair balm that treats 21 skin indication, such as: burns, mosquito bite, post procedures, and nappy rash\n\n• A complete formula with PANTHENOL (VITAMIN B5) to soothe the skin, SHEA BUTTER to nourish the skin barrier, MADECASSOSIDE to accelerate the repairing process\n\n• Ultra nourishing texture, non-greasy finish\n\n• Can be used on body, face and lips.\n\n • FRAGRANCE-FREE and PARABEN-FREE \n\n • Suitable for all skin types','balm, repairing, body cream,soothing, la roche posay body cream, Body moisturiser, Dry, Cicaplast','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,57,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
