ient. that helps to repair skin’s protective barrier in its different dimensions.\n• Immediate effectiveness : relieves from the first application.','lip balm, chapped lips, dry lips, la roche posay lip balm, moistrizer, Lip Care, Dry, Cicaplast','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,55,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
