nkles.\n• Perfect balance between peeling and soothing actions,','niacinamide serum, serum, acne serum , salicylic acid serum, la roche posay salicylic acid serum, acne serum, acne, peeling, acne marks, serum, Oily, Acne Prone skin, Effaclar','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,52,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
