en and could lead to hyperpigmentation (red or brown marks).\n• All the benefits of an spf 30 sunscreen with the sensoriality of a daily care in a fresh gel-cream texture.\n• Tested in environment with pollution peaks.\n• Fresh gel-cream, 24hr hydratation.','acne cream, pimple cream, moisturizer for acne prone skin, la roche posay acne treatment, Acne treatment, Oily, Acne Prone skin, Effaclar','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,50,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
