arks & imperfections.\n• Natural skin recovery in 1 HR.\n• reduces Itching.','acne cream, pimple cream, moisturizer for acne prone skin, la roche posay moisturiser for acne prone skin, oily skin moisturizer, roaccutane wash, isotretinoin wash, Moisturising  Cream, Oily/acne prone skin, Effaclar','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,49,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
