Anthelios','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,99,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('la-roche-posay-effaclar-purifying-gel-cleanser-f-11083','LA ROCHE-POSAY EFFACLAR PURIFYING GEL CLEANSER FOR OILY SKIN 200ML','La Roche-Posay','Face Care',14.97,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'la','Gently removes impurities & visibly reduces imperfections.','The La Roche Posay Effaclar Gel was developed with the help of microbiome science and works effectively on oily & acne-prone skin. The new active ingredient Phylobioma targets the overproduction of sebum at source & corrects imperfections. In addition, Zinc PCA also helps in reducing sebum and purifying the skin. Hence, Effaclar Gel purifies the skin while maintaining the skin\'s pH balance. Effaclar Gel gently removes impurities & visibly reduces imperfections, leaves the skin clean & refreshed and is suitable for oily & acne prone skin from age 10.','3337872411083','320M90544','200 ml','Use luke-warm water to help unclog pores. Foam in the hand and massage gently on the t-zone and neck. Work in circular strokes. Rinse off with cool water to help tighten pores.','AQUA / WATER, SODIUM LAURETH SULFATE, PEG-8, COCO-BETAINE, HEXYLENE GLYCOL, SODIUM CHLORIDE, PEG-120 METHYL GLUCOSE DIOLEATE, ZINC PCA, SODIUM HYDROXIDE, CITRIC ACID, SODIUM BENZOATE, PHENOXYETHANOL, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, PARFUM / FRAGRANCE','• Gently removes impurities & visibly reduces imperfections.\n• Leaves the skin clean and refreshed\n• Suitable for oily acne-prone and sensitive skin. From 10 YO.','Cleanser, Oily Skin','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,80,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
