 ingredient.\n•Dermatologically tested on sensitive skin, Lipikar Syndet AP+ Wash Cream is soap-free and fragrance-free.\n•Suitable even for newborns.','body wash, eczema body wash, baby body wash, la roche posay body wash, cream wash, cleanser, Body wash, Dry, Lipikar','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,43,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
