g cream, face cream, face moisturizer,  la roche posay moisturizing cream, sensitive skin, Moisturising  Cream, Sensitive, Toleriane','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,38,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
