LYACRYLATE - TOCOPHEROL - TRISODIUM ETHYLENEDIAMINE DISUCCINATE - VITREOSCILLA FERMENT - PERFUME / FRAGRANCE','','sunscreen, sun block, sunscreen for face, spf, sunblock cream,sun cream, tinted sunscreen, la roche posay sunscreen, anti-ageing, Capital soleil','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,100,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
