 for sensitive scalp','hair volume, hair thickening, Vichy hair thickening conditioner, Hair Thickening Conditioner, Thinning & Sparse hair, Dercos','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,16,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
