rol and vitamin E\n•With densifying Stemoxydine and Rhamnose\n•Tester under dermatological control, suitable for sensitive scalp','hair thickening, hair volume, hair thickening treatment, Vichy hair thickening treatment, Hair Thickening Treatment, Thinning & Sparse hair, Dercos','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,14,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
