all hair type\n•Hypoallergenic formula\n•Tested under dermatologicla control\n•Hair is nourished and more resistant to breakage','hair loss shampoo, hair fall shampoo, Vichy hair loss shampoo, Anti hair loss shampoo, All hair types, Dercos','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,13,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
