free, alcohol-free, no colorants\n•Hypoallergenic and tested on sensitive skin','niacinamide serum, anti aging serum, dark spot serum, Vichy Niacinamide serum, serum, All Skin Types, Liftactiv','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,37,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
