ible collagen loss signs. Increases firmness by 16% and extensibility by 17%.\n•Corrects uneven skin tone\n•Reduces wrinkles and boosts radiance\n•Long-lasting lifted feel\n•Skin feels softer and smoother\n•Non-greasy texture\n•Hypoallergenic and tested on sensitive skin','antiaging cream, vitamin c cream, night cream, Vichy Liftactiv Aging Night Cream, Antiaging face cream, All Types, Liftactiv','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,1,0,0,4,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
