SODIUM ACRYLOYLDIMETHYLTAURATE COPOLYMER - ETHYLHEXYL HYDROXYSTEARATE - POLYSORBATE 80 - PARFUM / FRAGRANCE','• Smooths the look of wrinkles, targets loss of firmness, and brightens the complexion.\n•Light yet comfortable texture that melts immediately into the skin and leaves skin feeling smooth and hydrated.\n• In  just 4 weeks, deep wrinkles appear corrected and skin feels more elastic.\n•Skin looks smoother and feels firmer, day after day\n•Suitable for dry skin\n•Free from parabens\n•Hypoallergenic','moisturizing cream, face cream, face moisturizer, anti aging cream, Vichy Liftactiv Anti Aging Day Cream, Antiaging face cream, All Types, Liftactiv','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,1,0,0,5,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
