ntours\n• Lightweight texture\n• Leaves the skin feeling smooth, plumped and youthful with a health-looking glow\n• Enriched with 1.5% Pure Hyaluronic Acid . Helps to plump, smooth and intensely hydrate skin\n• Offers up to 24-Hour Hydration\n• Clinically proven to strengthen the barrier function\n• Dermatologically tested and tested on post-procedure\n• Hypoallergenic','hyaluronic acid serum, anti aging serum, hyaluronic serum,eye serum, Vichy hyaluronic acid serum, serum, All Skin Types, Liftactiv','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,0,0,0,36,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
