min c serum for face, Vichy vitamin c serum, serum, All skin types, Liftactiv','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,1,0,0,8,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('vichy-mineral-89-hyaluronic-acid-hydrating-serum-for-all-skin-ty','Vichy Mineral 89 Hyaluronic Acid Hydrating Serum for All Skin Types 50ml','Vichy','Face Care',28.47,NULL,NULL,'',5.0,0,50,5,'mineral 89','+24% hydration after first use, +21% plumpness after 4 weeks','Vichy Mineral 89 Hyaluronic Acid Serum is formulated with 89% Vichy Mineralizing Water and Hyaluronic Acid. The hydrating serum enriches the skin with long-lasting moisture using a minimalist 11-ingredient formulation. It hydrates, plumps and fortifies the skin against daily aggressors such as pollution, stress, and fatigue. Skin is hydrated, radiant and moisturized. The lightweight gel texture creates a soothing veil upon application, helping to support the skin\'s natural barrier and defend against pollutants. Suitable for all skin types, even sensitive skin, the serum leaves the skin hydrated and provides a healthy-looking glow for up to 24 hours. Hypoallergenic, no fragrance, no alcohol.','3337875543248','322M91546','50 ml','Apply Mineral 89 as the 1st step of your daily routine on clean skin. Apply 2 drops on the fingertips. Tap gently back and forth to distribute over the face, then spread upward from the inside to the contours.','AQUA / WATER - PEG/PPG/POLYBUTYLENE GLYCOL-8/5/3 GLYCERIN - GLYCERIN - BUTYLENE GLYCOL - METHYL GLUCETH-20 - CARBOMER - SODIUM HYALURONATE - PHENOXYETHANOL - CAPRYLYL GLYCOL - CITRIC ACID - BIOSACCHARIDE GUM-1','+24% hydration after first use, +21% plumpness after 4 weeks\r\nStrengthens the skin barrier against daily aggressors\r\nSuitable for all skin types, tested on sensitive skin\r\nHydrates, plumps and tones the skin\r\nMore resistant to visible signs of aging (UV, pollution, stress)\r\nLightweight, fast-absorbing translucent booster\r\nFragrance-free, alcohol-free, hypoallergenic\r\n','hyaluronic acid serum, hydrating serum, hyaluronic serum, vichy mineral 89, serum, all skin types','uploads/20260708-233244-ad55bb3a.jpg','uploads/20260708-233246-7b041c5f.jpg','uploads/20260708-233349-4044caee.jpg\nuploads/20260708-233531-224fa716.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000733-b8d3d1ef.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000733-1ff45472.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000752-ba31c55a.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000752-63797640.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000752-12c1cc49.jpg\nuploads/20260709-000752-e5a128a7.jpg',0,0,0,0,'active','2026-07-08 20:32:46');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('vichy-mineralizing-thermal-water-hydrating-face--08612','Vichy Mineralizing Thermal Water, Hydrating Face Mist with Natural Antioxidants  150ml','Vichy','Face Care',11.37,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'eau thermale vichy','Strengthen skin\'s moisture barrier','Vichy’s Mineralizing Thermal Water is born in the French volcanoes and travels to depths of up to 4000 meters before it is heated to 140C and thrust up to the surface. Over the course of its thousand-year journey, it absorbs 15 minerals which give the water its power.With 11 tests and 5 clinical studies, Vichy’s Mineralizing Thermal Water mist has been clinically proven to strengthen the skin’s barrier function and help accelerate surface skin cell renewal. It helps soothe the feel of skin exposed to external aggressors and leaves it looking healthy and glowing. A 100% pure, natural active ingredient, hypoallergenic, fragrance-free, no preservatives.','3337871308612','322M50289','150 ml','Apply to skin in a fine mist. Wait for a few moments and gently pat dry.\nA daily care product to be used at any time during the day or evening.','AQUA / WATER','•Strengthen skin\'s moisture barrier\n•Protect skin from external aggresors\n•Healthy  and glowing looking skin\n•Suitable for sensitve skin\n•Formulated with Vichy 15 minerals','face mist, facial spray, face mist spray, Vichy Hydrating Face Mist, face mist moisturizer, sensitive skin, Eau Thermale Vichy','uploads/prod-3337871308612-1.jpg','uploads/prod-3337871308612-2.jpg',NULL,1,0,0,0,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('vichy-normaderm-3-in-1-cleanser-scrub-mask-for-o-14067','Vichy Normaderm 3 in 1 Cleanser, Scrub & Mask for Oily/Acne Skin with salicylic  & glycolic acid 125ml','Vichy','Face Care',19.44,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'normaderm','Exfoliator: helps unclog pores.','Vichy Normaderm\'s 3-in-1 Cleansing + Scrub + Mask is a one-stop solution for oily and imperfection-prone skin. When skin produces too much oil and becomes overburdened, clogged and imperfection-prone, it needs gentle care to make it feel fresh and comfortable again. Normaderm\'s 3-in-1 Cleansing + Scrub + Mask combined cleanse, scrub and mask action is rich in soothing properties and clarified Clay, making it perfect for even sensitive skin.Use Normaderm\'s 3-in-1 Cleansing + Scrub + Mask as a cleanser by lathering onto a damp face and rinsing off with plenty of water. Alternatively, use the cream as a daily scrub to unclog pores, and make the texture of the skin more uniform, or use as a mask once a week to intensely cleanse and remove dead skin cells. Apply in a thick layer and leave on for 5 minutes before rinsing away thoroughly. Avoid the eye contour.','3337875414067','322M97215','125 ml','As a cleanser/scrub: lather onto damp face and rinse off with plenty of water. As a mask: twice a week, apply a thin layer to the face and leave to dry for 5 minutes. Rinse with clear water. Avoid the eye contour.','AQUA - KAOLIN - BUTYLENE GLYCOL - ZEA MAYS STARCH - GLYCERIN - DECYL GLUCOSIDE - CI 77891 - CARRAGEENAN - PEG-7 GLYCERYL COCOATE - CI 77288 - GLYCOLIC ACID - ZINC GLUCONATE - PUMICE - SILICA [NANO] - SALICYLIC ACID - SODIUM HYDROXIDE - SODIUM CHLORIDE - PHENOXYETHANOL - COCO-BETAINE - DIPOTASSIUM GLYCYRRHIZATE - DISODIUM EDTA - XANTHAN GUM - PARFUM','•Exfoliator: helps unclog pores.\n•Cleansing cream: reduces sebum and impurities.\n•Mask: matifies skin and clarifies complexion.\n•Impurities and excess sebum are removed\n•Intensely cleanses and removes dead skin cells\n•Skin is left feeling soothed, fresh and comfortable\n•Suitable for sensitive skin\n•Hypoallergenic','cleanser with salicylic acid, salicylic acid face wash, face wash for oily skin, acne face wash, oily skin cleanser, cleansing gel, Vichy Normaderm Cleanser, oily skin cleanser, oily skin, Normaderm','uploads/photo-pending.png','',NULL,1,0,0,3,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `category`, `price`, `was`, `sale_pct`, `badge`, `rating`, `reviews`, `stock`, `low_stock`, `kw`, `descr`, `long_desc`, `barcode`, `sku`, `size`, `how_to_use`, `ingredients`, `benefits`, `keywords`, `image`, `hover_image`, `gallery`, `feat_latest`, `feat_wellness`, `home_sort`, `sort`, `status`, `created_at`) VALUES ('vichy-normaderm-phytosolution-face-cleanser-gel--63076','Vichy Normaderm Phytosolution Face Cleanser Gel for Oily/Acne Skin with Salicylic Acid 200ml','Vichy','Face Care',16.01,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'normaderm','After the first wash, 91% of dirt and pollution are removed','Vichy Normaderm Phytosolution Purifying Cleansing Gel is a daily gel cleanser that purifies and revitalises the appearance of oily, blemish-prone skin. Perfectly removes impurities including dirt, dust and pollutant particles while clearing clogged pores and blackheads so skin feels cleansed and is left looking fresher, clearer and mattified. In just one month, blackheads appear less prominent and pores look unclogged. Suitable for sensitive skin. Dermatologically tested. Hypoallergenic. Enriched with actives including Salicylic Acid and Zinc Gluconate, in a cleansing base from plant origin. Clinically proven efficacy on excess oil.','3337875663076','322MB1582','200 ml','Morning and evening rub product onto wet face, until it foams. Rinse off. Avoid the skin around the eyes. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water.','AQUA /WATER - COCO-BETAINE - PROPANEDIOL - PEG-120 METHYL GLUCOSE DIOLEATE - SODIUM CHLORIDE - SODIUM COCOYL GLYCINATE - DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL - ZINC GLUCONATE - SALICYLIC ACID - BIFIDA FERMENT LYSATE - SODIUM HYDROXIDE - SODIUM BENZOATE - PHENOXYETHANOL - COPPER GLUCONATE - CAPRYLYL GLYCOL - TETRASODIUM GLUTAMATE DIACETATE - PARFUM / FRAGRANCE','•After the first wash, 91% of dirt and pollution are removed\n•After the first wash, 94% off excess of serum reduced\n•83% of skin texture appeards refinedand 98% of marks due to imperfections look reduced after 4 weeks\n•Skin is purified\n•No drying-up\n•Hypoallergenic, suitable for sensitive skin\n•Tested under dermatological control','cleanser with salicylic acid, salicylic acid face wash, face wash for oily skin, acne face wash, oily skin cleanser, cleansing gel, Vichy Normaderm Cleanser Gel, oily skin cleanser, oily skin, Normaderm','uploads/prod-3337875663076-1.jpg','uploads/prod-3337875663076-2.jpg','uploads/prod-3337875663076-g3.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875663076-g4.jpg',1,0,0,2,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
