edand 98% of marks due to imperfections look reduced after 4 weeks\n•Skin is purified\n•No drying-up\n•Hypoallergenic, suitable for sensitive skin\n•Tested under dermatological control','cleanser with salicylic acid, salicylic acid face wash, face wash for oily skin, acne face wash, oily skin cleanser, cleansing gel, Vichy Normaderm Cleanser Gel, oily skin cleanser, oily skin, Normaderm','uploads/prod-3337875663083-1.jpg','uploads/prod-3337875663083-2.png','uploads/prod-3337875663083-g3.png\nuploads/prod-3337875663083-g4.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875663083-g5.jpg',1,0,0,1,'active','2026-07-08 09:35:13');
